Description: Ashampoo Burning Studio - new version of the program for recording CD-RW, DVD-RW, DVD RW and Blu-ray discs last line of the package. The utility allows you to create projects and record CD / DVD (including MP3-CD, VCD, S-VCD and Blu-ray). The program supports long filenames (127 characters for DVD and Blu-ray and 64 for CD), automatic configuration settings, saving and loading project, the creation of images, simple file management with DragandDrop and more. Works with most recording devices. It has never been so easy to convert your files to DVD discs that can be played on any DVD-player.

